# ☁️ Basic MERN Task Manager

A simple full-stack task manager built with the **MERN stack**: MongoDB, Express.js, React, and Node.js.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add, update, and delete tasks
- ⚡ Real-time UI updates with Redux Toolkit
- 🗃️ MongoDB integration (local or MongoDB Atlas)
- 🌐 RESTful API powered by Express.js

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend**  
- React.js  
- Bootstrap  
- Redux Toolkit (for state management)

**Backend**  
- Node.js  
- Express.js  

**Database**  
- MongoDB (Local or hosted on [MongoDB Atlas](https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas))

